<p><strong>The Tenth City: Land of Elyon 3 by Patrick Carman</strong></p>
<p><strong>What is the "Tenth City"?</strong></p>
<p>The Tenth City is a mystical and enigmatic realm that lies beyond the physical world. It is a place where the laws of nature do not apply, and where magic and wonder intertwine.</p>
<p><strong>Who is Patrick Carman?</strong></p>
<p>Patrick Carman is an award-winning American author who specializes in young adult fantasy novels. He is best known for his series "The Land of Elyon," which includes "The Tenth City."</p>
<p><strong>What is the PDF format?</strong></p>
<p>The PDF (Portable Document Format) is a file format that allows documents to be shared and viewed across multiple platforms. It is used to preserve the original formatting and layout of a document.</p>
