<p>The PDF of "The Tenth City" can be found on various websites, including Amazon and Barnes &amp; Noble. It is also available on the official website of Patrick Carman.</p>
<p><strong>What is the significance of "The Tenth City" in the series?</strong></p>
<p>The Tenth City plays a crucial role in the "Land of Elyon" series. It is the setting for the third book, where the protagonist must confront his destiny and the fate of both the physical and mystical realms.</p>